sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.cdbg

Interface BlockSym

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Sym
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FunctionSym
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicBlockSym, BasicFunctionSym, LazyBlockSym

    public interface BlockSym
extends Sym
    A BlockSym models a lexical scope in a block-structured language. It is (currently) the bottommost scope type.
